{
  "title": "SLB(Server Load Balancer)",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"quiver-file-url/6B6C2CB780B9FA6D068303E8EC062252.pptx\">SLB课件.pptx</a><br></font></div><div><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"quiver-file-url/592F8604902F565DDC592456DA0AE22E.docx\">SLB主要事项.docx</a><br></font></div><div><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"quiver-file-url/B75FE40B521F54747112EB85F1081F63.docx\">CRT证书转PEM证书.docx</a><br></font></div><div><a href=\"quiver-file-url/FF858694445570BB0405191320696BD3.docx\"><font color=\"#000000\">单个SLB单个端口实现多个站点搭建.docx</font></a></div><div><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"quiver-file-url/6ED7BF5610CDF32D8F5B3125E5ED83C8.docx\">利用RASYN实现SLB下ECS数据同步.docx</a><br></font></div><div><font color=\"#000000\">适合作为流量的入口</font></div><div><font color=\"#000000\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/10ACDC3AC51E790B6DC20899A8D9D902.jpg\"><br></font></div><div><font color=\"#000000\">解决的问题：</font></div><div><ul><li><font color=\"#000000\">随着业务的发展，单一服务器无法满足系统容量问题</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">升级硬件投入成本太高</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">如果业务继续增长，那么如何满足扩容问题</font></li></ul><div><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">应用程序的无状态，一个客户端的请求，在其请求完成后，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\"><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%AB%AF&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1Y4mH0vnhwBmW9hmhD3nh7B0ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6K1TL0qnfK1TL0z5HD0IgF_5y9YIZ0lQzqlpA-bmyt8mh7GuZR8mvqVQL7dugPYpyq8Q1fsnjb3PWf1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">服务器端</a></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">都会删除这个请求的相关信息。有时我们需要</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">请求完成后，还要继续保持信息，在传统的</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">编程中最常用的有两种方式：</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Session</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Cookies</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">，但是这两种传统的方式，都有其弊端，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Session</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">会增加服务器的负担，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Cookies</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">则会依赖客户端，要求客户端必须支持</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Cookies</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">，同时</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">Cookies</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\">是存在客户端的计算机上，所以可能有安全问题。</span><br></font></div></div><div><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 17.1428px; widows: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></span></div><font color=\"#000000\">特点：</font><div><ol><li><font color=\"#000000\">高可用</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">底层本（私有网络类型的SLB的负载均衡免费使用）</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">无需运维投入</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">安全（结合了云盾牌，能阻隔DDOS攻击）</font></li></ol><div><font color=\"#000000\">应用场景：</font></div></div><div><ol><li><font color=\"#000000\">公网负载均衡</font></li><li><font color=\"#000000\">内网服务需要负载均衡</font></li></ol></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/F1A1FE8114DB58457CF212CC1D1C74F6.jpg\"><b><br></b></div><b>SLB的基本概念：</b><div><ul><li>SLB是对多台服务器将流量分发到云服务器上</li><li>将多态云服务器ECS构成一个资源池，虚拟成一个高可用性的服务池</li><li>SLB会自动检测ECS服务器的健康状态，自动隔离异常状态的ECS，同时提高应用的服务能力</li><li>提供了基于TCP和HTTP防DDOS攻击</li><li>SLB会存在于一个Zone下，但是却可以为整个Region提供负载均衡服务</li></ul><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/DE3C13DAD044A0AB063D1096621FBFF3.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/F8D5050C1AC46B73343430A7FEE6A1FC.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/006D2693AB10FB9E39553420A2EB2906.jpg\"><br></div><div><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/40E630C378F6D97EAD73F59A9418B5E0.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/CF15CFA8DC927CA97DFA50B23BC702CC.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/D4EEFE30D848C1C48500D9FB8454926F.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/63CD6536F8AC3FB558C87A327643A974.jpg\"><br></div><div><img src=\"quiver-image-url/9D5A7601109C2A86C67EA261EE6F4FCC.jpg\"><br></div><div><b>SLB如何容灾：</b></div></div><div><ol><li>一个SLB可以添加一个Region下面的多个可用区的ECS（将ECS实例分布在多个可用区）</li><li>SLB实例可以在一个Region的多个Zone之间切换（自动进行，不需要人工干预）</li><li>在一个Region下创建多个SLB实例，通过DNS轮询的方式提供对外服务，也可以提高本地可用性</li><li>在不同的Region创建SLB实例，通过DNS轮询的方式对外提供服务，可以提高跨Region的可用性</li></ol></div>"
    },
    {
